data.description: Country Charmer! What a lovely Country Home! A perfect place to raise your family! Lovely neighborhood with lots of room for children to ride their bikes! This seller has put so much work and character into this home it is a one of a kind! You will love all the woodwork and charm! Lovely paint colors and feels like home as soon as you walk in. The foyer is so quaint as you walk in. The living room has nice large front windows and is open to the dinning room area with large wood fireplace and has fantastic wood shelving on each side of the fireplace! Wood laminate flooring great ceiling fan and is so cozy and ready for a family to call their home! The kitchen has newly painted cabin with a touch of wood uppers! Granite countertops and just perfect for the mom that likes to can with all the shelving! The bedrooms are nice size with great colors. The master bedroom has a master shower and large closet! Also the master has a cozy  nook. And slider doors to walk out on your nice deck! The downstairs has a large laundry and pantry area that goes out to the garage and to the mans workshop inside the garage. This home has a huge fully fenced back yard , plenty of room for the kids  to play
